// Notification Store
// Zustand store for managing in-app toast notifications.
// Supports auto-dismissal via duration and manual removal.

State shape:
  toasts: Toast[]
  Each Toast has: id (toast_<timestamp>_<hex4>), type, title, message, duration, timestamp.

FUNCTION addToast(toast) -> id                                          EXPORT
  Generate a unique ID in the format toast_<timestamp>_<randomHex4>.
  Add the full toast object to the toasts array.
  IF toast.duration > 0, schedule auto-removal after that many milliseconds.
  Return the generated ID.

---

FUNCTION removeToast(id)                                                EXPORT
  Filter toasts to remove the one with the matching ID.

---

FUNCTION clearAll()                                                     EXPORT
  Set toasts to an empty array.
